question:
某电商平台开发秒杀商品的库存扣减服务，具体需求与约束如下：1. 秒杀商品总库存固定为1000件，单个用户ID限购1件；2. 订单创建后30分钟未支付则自动取消，取消后需回滚对应库存；3. 技术栈为SpringBoot+MySQL，事务隔离级别设置为READ_COMMITTED，库存扣减采用乐观锁（version版本号）实现；4. 接口需支持10000 QPS的并发请求，不允许出现超卖、少卖、库存为负、用户重复购买的情况。现给出核心业务代码如下：
@Service
public class SeckillService {
    @Autowired
    private StockMapper stockMapper;
    @Autowired
    private OrderMapper orderMapper;
    // 内存定时线程池，用于处理订单超时取消
    private ScheduledExecutorService scheduledExecutor = Executors.newScheduledThreadPool(10);

    @Transactional(rollbackFor = Exception.class)
    public String seckill(Long userId, Long goodsId) {
        // 步骤1：校验用户是否已购买过该商品
        Integer count = orderMapper.selectCountByUserAndGoods(userId, goodsId, "已支付,已取消");
        if (count > 0) {
            return "您已购买过该商品";
        }
        // 步骤2：扣减库存
        Stock stock = stockMapper.selectByGoodsId(goodsId);
        if (stock.getStock() <= 0) {
            return "库存不足";
        }
        int updateRows = stockMapper.updateStock(goodsId, stock.getVersion());
        if (updateRows == 0) {
            // 乐观锁冲突重试，最多重试3次
            for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
                stock = stockMapper.selectByGoodsId(goodsId);
                if (stock.getStock() <= 0) {
                    return "库存不足";
                }
                updateRows = stockMapper.updateStock(goodsId, stock.getVersion());
                if (updateRows > 0) {
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (updateRows == 0) {
                return "操作繁忙，请重试";
            }
        }
        // 步骤3：生成待支付订单
        Order order = new Order();
        order.setUserId(userId);
        order.setGoodsId(goodsId);
        order.setStatus("待支付");
        orderMapper.insert(order);
        // 步骤4：提交30分钟超时取消任务
        scheduledExecutor.schedule(() -> cancelOrder(order.getId()), 30, TimeUnit.MINUTES);
        return "秒杀成功，请在30分钟内支付";
    }

    @Transactional(rollbackFor = Exception.class)
    public void cancelOrder(Long orderId) {
        Order order = orderMapper.selectById(orderId);
        // 仅处理待支付订单
        if (order == null || !"待支付".equals(order.getStatus())) {
            return;
        }
        // 更新订单状态为已取消
        order.setStatus("已取消");
        orderMapper.updateById(order);
        // 回滚库存
        stockMapper.incrStock(order.getGoodsId());
    }
}
// Mapper层核心SQL：
// 1. updateStock对应SQL：update seckill_stock set stock = stock - 1, version = version + 1 where goods_id = #{goodsId} and version = #{version} and stock > 0
// 2. incrStock对应SQL：update seckill_stock set stock = stock + 1 where goods_id = #{goodsId}
// 3. selectCountByUserAndGoods对应SQL：select count(*) from seckill_order where user_id = #{userId} and goods_id = #{goodsId} and status in ('已支付','已取消')
要求：请定位代码中所有与边界条件、异常处理相关的微妙错误，说明每个错误触发的具体场景、导致的后果，以及修复方案，需至少经过5步推理过程才能完全定位所有错误。
